    "Finally, √ d is used as a regularisation technique with d being the dimension of K i.",
    "Using the Hadamard product essentially zeroes out the attention between regions whose relationship is not being processed by that sub-layer.",
    "The resulting encodings are decoded by an LSTM to produce captions.Like [60], the M2 meshed memory Transformer proposed by Cornia et al. [59] also makes use of the increasingly popular Transformer architecture [40].",
    "Unlike other papers [39,58,60,87] which make use of some predefined structure on extracted image features (spatial graph, semantic graph, etc.",
    "), M2 uses stacks of self-attention layers across the set of all the image regions."
